OL,3,CBaby hospice to close after 30 years
OL,5,FA specialist baby hospice says it will
OL,6,Fbe closing down at the end of the year
OL,7,Fafter failing to find funding for a
OL,8,Fnew building before its lease runs out.
OL,10,FZoe's Place has been in operation for
OL,11,Fthe last 30 years and had hoped to
OL,12,Fbuild a new #3.5m hospice close to its
OL,13,Fcurrent location in Yew Tree Lane,
OL,14,FLiverpool.
OL,16,FBut, a statement from the trustees
OL,17,Freleased on 7 October, said: "The time
OL,18,Ftaken to get planning permission has
OL,19,Fleft insufficient time to construct
OL,20,Fthe building.
