OL,5,FMatt Meany, head of fundraising for
OL,6,FZoe's Place, said the service the
OL,7,Fhospice provides is a "lifeline for
OL,8,Ffamilies."
OL,10,F"They rely on us - and they're going
OL,11,Fto lose that support that we've
OL,12,Fprovided in Liverpool for nearly 30
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FMatt says the hospice has simply "ran
OL,16,Fout of time", adding: "For this to be
OL,17,Fmiraculously fixed, we need someone to
OL,18,Fcome to us with a building and say
OL,19,F'you can have this'.
