OL,3,CBaby hospice to close after 30 years
OL,5,F"It is absolutely devastating to have
OL,6,Fthese conversations, particularly with
OL,7,Fthe families.
OL,9,F"Everyone in this organisation has
OL,10,Fchosen to work in the charity sector
OL,11,Fbecause they believe in what we do. To
OL,12,Fsee it end is something we never
OL,13,Fdreamed of happening.
OL,15,F"I know that everyone in this
OL,16,Forganisation has fought hard to keep
OL,17,Fthis going and find a solution."
