OL,3,CBaby hospice to close after 30 years
OL,5,FChildren's hospice Claire House, which
OL,6,Fhas bases in Wirral and in West Derby,
OL,7,Fsay they closure of Zoe's Place is
OL,8,Fconcerning.
OL,10,FDavid Pastor, CEO at Claire House,
OL,11,Fsaid: "We were deeply saddened when we
OL,12,Fheard about the closure of Zoe's Place
OL,13,Fand are concerned for all the
OL,14,Fchildren, families and staff affected.
OL,16,F"As it stands, we know there are not
OL,17,Fenough services for seriously and
OL,18,Fterminally ill children in the area,
OL,19,Fand this will just make the situation
OL,20,Fworse."
